[{"title":"Ubuntu环境部署代理","url":"/2025/12/12/Ubuntu%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86/","content":"<h4 id=\"1、浏览器搜索clash-premium内核下载\"><a href=\"#1、浏览器搜索clash-premium内核下载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1、浏览器搜索clash premium内核下载\"></a>1、浏览器搜索clash premium内核下载</h4><p>提前在Windows环境下载号Linux版本的clash内核，拷贝到Linux环境下</p>\n<p>下载网址：<a href=\"https://down.clash.la/Clash/Core/Premium/clash-linux-amd64-latest.gz\">https://down.clash.la/Clash/Core/Premium/clash-linux-amd64-latest.gz</a></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h4 id=\"2、解压并安装\"><a href=\"#2、解压并安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2、解压并安装\"></a>2、解压并安装</h4><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">解压</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">gzip -d clash-linux-amd64-2023.09.08.gz</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">重命名为clash，并赋予执行权限</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">mv clash-linux-amd64-2023.09.08 clash</span><br><span class=\"line\">chmod +x clash</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">将clash拷贝到系统Path目录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo cp clash /usr/local/bin/</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">验证安装是否成功</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">clash -v  # 输出版本信息表示安装成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"3、部署配置文件\"><a href=\"#3、部署配置文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3、部署配置文件\"></a>3、部署配置文件</h4><ul>\n<li><p>配置文件默认路径为<code>~/.config/clash/config.yaml</code>，若没有该文件提前手动创建</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>打开Windows下的Clash软件，在订阅右上角点击查看运行时订阅</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/clash%E7%9A%84config%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F.png\" alt=\"config获取方式\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>将里面的全部内容写入<code>~/.config/clash/config.yaml</code>文件中</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"4、运行Clash软件\"><a href=\"#4、运行Clash软件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4、运行Clash软件\"></a>4、运行Clash软件</h4><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">终端前台运行clash，关闭终端就会关闭clash</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">clash</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">后台运行clash</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">clash &amp;   # 若想关闭clash需要执行命令slay -9 clash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"5、部署一键配置终端代理\"><a href=\"#5、部署一键配置终端代理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5、部署一键配置终端代理\"></a>5、部署一键配置终端代理</h4><p>创建<code>proxy.sh</code>脚本文件，内容如下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\">#</span><span class=\"language-bash\">!/bin/bash</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">代理设置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">PROXY_HOST=&quot;127.0.0.1&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">PROXY_PORT=&quot;7897&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">设置代理函数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">set_proxy() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    export http_proxy=&quot;http://$&#123;PROXY_HOST&#125;:$&#123;PROXY_PORT&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    export https_proxy=&quot;http://$&#123;PROXY_HOST&#125;:$&#123;PROXY_PORT&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    export HTTP_PROXY=&quot;http://$&#123;PROXY_HOST&#125;:$&#123;PROXY_PORT&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    export HTTPS_PROXY=&quot;http://$&#123;PROXY_HOST&#125;:$&#123;PROXY_PORT&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    export ALL_PROXY=&quot;socks5://$&#123;PROXY_HOST&#125;:$&#123;PROXY_PORT&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    export all_proxy=&quot;socks5://$&#123;PROXY_HOST&#125;:$&#123;PROXY_PORT&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    # 设置git代理</span><br><span class=\"line\">    git config --global http.proxy &quot;http://$&#123;PROXY_HOST&#125;:$&#123;PROXY_PORT&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    git config --global https.proxy &quot;http://$&#123;PROXY_HOST&#125;:$&#123;PROXY_PORT&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;✅ 代理已开启: $&#123;PROXY_HOST&#125;:$&#123;PROXY_PORT&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;当前代理设置:&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;http_proxy=$http_proxy&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;https_proxy=$https_proxy&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">取消代理函数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">unset_proxy() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    unset http_proxy</span><br><span class=\"line\">    unset https_proxy</span><br><span class=\"line\">    unset HTTP_PROXY</span><br><span class=\"line\">    unset HTTPS_PROXY</span><br><span class=\"line\">    unset ALL_PROXY</span><br><span class=\"line\">    unset all_proxy</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    # 取消git代理</span><br><span class=\"line\">    git config --global --unset http.proxy</span><br><span class=\"line\">    git config --global --unset https.proxy</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;✅ 代理已关闭&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">显示帮助信息</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">show_help() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;用法: $0 [0|1]&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;  0: 关闭代理&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;  1: 开启代理&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;  不带参数: 显示当前代理状态&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">显示当前代理状态</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">show_status() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;当前代理状态:&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;http_proxy=$&#123;http_proxy:-未设置&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;https_proxy=$&#123;https_proxy:-未设置&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo &quot;ALL_PROXY=$&#123;ALL_PROXY:-未设置&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    git_proxy=$(git config --global http.proxy)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if [ -n &quot;$git_proxy&quot; ]; then</span><br><span class=\"line\">        echo &quot;Git代理: 已设置 ($git_proxy)&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    else</span><br><span class=\"line\">        echo &quot;Git代理: 未设置&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    fi</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">根据参数执行操作</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">case &quot;$1&quot; in</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;1&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        set_proxy</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;0&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        unset_proxy</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        show_status</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;-h&quot;|&quot;--help&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        show_help</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    *)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        echo &quot;错误: 参数无效&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        show_help</span><br><span class=\"line\">        exit 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">esac</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>在<code>~/.bashrc</code>中设置别名，方便使用，打开<code>.bashrc</code>，在最后加上</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">设置别名</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">alias proxy=&quot;source proxy.sh&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">使环境变量立即生效</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">source ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>使用方式</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">开启终端代理</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">proxy 1</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">查看终端代理</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">proxy</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">关闭终端代理</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">proxy 0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"6、附录\"><a href=\"#6、附录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6、附录\"></a>6、附录</h4><p>参考资料：<a href=\"https://geek-blogs.com/blog/clash-for-for-linux/\">https://geek-blogs.com/blog/clash-for-for-linux/</a></p>\n","categories":["工具"],"tags":["Ubuntu"]},{"title":"Hello World","url":"/2025/12/12/hello-world/","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n"}]